{"tid":2137029,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★有消息指 Apple 在中國 App Store 移除了接近 3 萬個 App","createTime":"2020-08-02T14:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T14:46:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d06496f15582868606fb2283ef6f48a2b6e09f4d","tid":2137029,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:42:25.000Z","msg":"中國政府對於媒體和遊戲的審核都相當嚴格，最近有消息指 Apple 在中國 App Store 移除了接近 3 萬個 App，其中大部分是未獲政府批核的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n據七麥數據的調查指，繼 7 月初移除 2,500 個遊戲之後，上星期六 Apple 在中國 App Store 再次一舉移除了 29,800 個 App，其中 26,000 個為遊戲類別，據稱這是與中國政府近日嚴格打擊未批核遊戲有關，在今年較早前 Apple 曾經向遊戲開發商發出警告，表示他們如果希望在作品加入 App 內購買項目，則必須提供政府的審核編號。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/08/02/apple-removes-thousands-of-game-apps-from-china-store/software/ios-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F08%2F02%2Fapple-removes-thousands-of-game-apps-from-china-store%2Fsoftware%2Fios-app%2F&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F9lAIsOV5GGnQ0mU6qdzh4w%3D&h=58f3a370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/08/02/apple-removes-thousands-of-game-apps-from-china-store/software/ios-app/</a>"},{"pid":"358e47dd552bef8ed8e75edcbebb5e22c0aedf03","tid":2137029,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0db4206b05a239416126a1a356a6504ba615ab3b","tid":2137029,"uid":83713,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T14:43:53.000Z","msg":"大陸班韮菜係咪就嚟冇game玩<img src=\"/assets/f